{"paragraphs":[{"cues":[{"time":1478,"text":"Francesca Fedeli: Ciao."},{"time":3375,"text":"So he's Mario. He's our son."},{"time":6931,"text":"He was born two and a half years ago,"},{"time":9790,"text":"and I had a pretty tough pregnancy"},{"time":13003,"text":"because I had to stay still\nin a bed for, like, eight months."},{"time":17153,"text":"But in the end everything\nseemed to be under control."},{"time":20212,"text":"So he got the right weight at birth."},{"time":23066,"text":"He got the right Apgar index."},{"time":25213,"text":"So we were pretty reassured by this."},{"time":28298,"text":"But at the end, 10 days\nlater after he was born,"},{"time":35150,"text":"we discovered that he had a stroke."},{"time":37697,"text":"As you might know,"},{"time":39567,"text":"a stroke is a brain injury."},{"time":42133,"text":"A perinatal stroke could be something"},{"time":44843,"text":"that can happen\nduring the nine months of pregnancy"},{"time":48758,"text":"or just suddenly after the birth,"},{"time":51350,"text":"and in his case, as you can see,"},{"time":54247,"text":"the right part of his brain has gone."},{"time":58439,"text":"So the effect that this stroke\ncould have on Mario's body"},{"time":63930,"text":"could be the fact that he couldn't\nbe able to control"},{"time":67174,"text":"the left side of his body."},{"time":69950,"text":"Just imagine, if you have\na computer and a printer"},{"time":73775,"text":"and you want to transmit,\nto input to print out a document,"},{"time":77964,"text":"but the printer doesn't\nhave the right drives,"},{"time":81408,"text":"so the same is for Mario."},{"time":84192,"text":"It's just like,\nhe would like to move his left side"},{"time":87212,"text":"of his body, but he's not able\nto transmit the right input"},{"time":91155,"text":"to move his left arm and left leg."},{"time":96035,"text":"So life had to change."},{"time":98277,"text":"We needed to change our schedule."},{"time":100316,"text":"We needed to change the impact\nthat this birth had"},{"time":106227,"text":"on our life."},{"time":108938,"text":"Roberto D'Angelo: As you may imagine,"},{"time":110940,"text":"unfortunately, we were not ready."},{"time":113236,"text":"Nobody taught us how to deal\nwith such kinds of disabilities,"},{"time":117291,"text":"and as many questions as possible started"},{"time":119378,"text":"to come to our minds."},{"time":121310,"text":"And that has been really a tough time."},{"time":124339,"text":"Questions, some basics, like, you know,"},{"time":126636,"text":"why did this happen to us?"},{"time":128816,"text":"And what went wrong?"},{"time":130811,"text":"Some more tough, like, really,"},{"time":133314,"text":"what will be the impact on Mario's life?"},{"time":135021,"text":"I mean, at the end,\nwill he be able to work?"},{"time":137141,"text":"Will he be able to be normal?"},{"time":138595,"text":"And, you know, as a parent,\nespecially for the first time,"},{"time":141820,"text":"why is he not going to be better than us?"},{"time":145262,"text":"And this, indeed, really is tough to say,"},{"time":148540,"text":"but a few months later, we realized that"},{"time":151328,"text":"we were really feeling like a failure."},{"time":154588,"text":"I mean, the only real product of our life,"},{"time":157609,"text":"at the end, was a failure."},{"time":159449,"text":"And you know, it was not a failure\nfor ourselves in itself,"},{"time":165375,"text":"but it was a failure\nthat will impact his full life."},{"time":170113,"text":"Honestly, we went down."},{"time":171887,"text":"I mean we went really\ndown, but at the end,"},{"time":175422,"text":"we started to look at him,"},{"time":177316,"text":"and we said, we have to react."},{"time":179565,"text":"So immediately, as Francesca\nsaid, we changed our life."},{"time":182443,"text":"We started physiotherapy,\nwe started the rehabilitation,"},{"time":185900,"text":"and one of the paths\nthat we were following"},{"time":187972,"text":"in terms of rehabilitation\nis the mirror neurons pilot."},{"time":190977,"text":"Basically, we spent months\ndoing this with Mario."},{"time":194768,"text":"You have an object, and we showed him"},{"time":197613,"text":"how to grab the object."},{"time":199634,"text":"Now, the theory of mirror\nneurons simply says"},{"time":202218,"text":"that in your brains, exactly\nnow, as you watch me doing this,"},{"time":206390,"text":"you are activating\nexactly the same neurons"},{"time":208900,"text":"as if you do the actions."},{"time":212137,"text":"It looks like this is the leading\nedge in terms of rehabilitation."},{"time":216133,"text":"But one day we found that Mario"},{"time":219985,"text":"was not looking at our hand."},{"time":223360,"text":"He was looking at us."},{"time":225934,"text":"We were his mirror."},{"time":228129,"text":"And the problem, as you might feel,"},{"time":230177,"text":"is that we were down, we were depressed,"},{"time":232622,"text":"we were looking at him as a problem,"},{"time":234994,"text":"not as a son, not\nfrom a positive perspective."},{"time":239499,"text":"And that day really\nchanged our perspective."},{"time":242739,"text":"We realized that we had to become"},{"time":246059,"text":"a better mirror for Mario."},{"time":248626,"text":"We restarted from our strengths,"},{"time":250714,"text":"and at the same time\nwe restarted from his strengths."},{"time":254417,"text":"We stopped looking at him as a problem,"},{"time":257115,"text":"and we started to look at him\nas an opportunity to improve."},{"time":261515,"text":"And really, this was the change,"},{"time":264073,"text":"and from our side, we said,"},{"time":267232,"text":"\"What are our strengths\nthat we really can bring to Mario?\""},{"time":270379,"text":"And we started from our passions."},{"time":271975,"text":"I mean, at the end, my wife and myself"},{"time":273809,"text":"are quite different,"},{"time":275033,"text":"but we have many things in common."},{"time":277121,"text":"We love to travel, we love music,"},{"time":279343,"text":"we love to be in places like this,"},{"time":281184,"text":"and we started to bring Mario with us"},{"time":283269,"text":"just to show to him the best\nthings that we can show to him."},{"time":287967,"text":"This short video is from last week."},{"time":293168,"text":"I am not saying --"},{"time":294773,"text":"(Applause) —"},{"time":296618,"text":"I am not saying it's a miracle.\nThat's not the message,"},{"time":299262,"text":"because we are just\nat the beginning of the path."},{"time":301811,"text":"But we want to share\nwhat was the key learning,"},{"time":305433,"text":"the key learning that Mario drove to us,"},{"time":307715,"text":"and it is to consider\nwhat you have as a gift"},{"time":310059,"text":"and not only what you miss,"},{"time":314747,"text":"and to consider what you\nmiss just as an opportunity."},{"time":318940,"text":"And this is the message\nthat we want to share with you."},{"time":321584,"text":"This is why we are here."},{"time":325320,"text":"Mario!"},{"time":327235,"text":"And this is why --"},{"time":328998,"text":"(Applause) —"},{"time":333600,"text":"And this is why"},{"time":338822,"text":"we decided to share the best\nmirror in the world with him."},{"time":344308,"text":"And we thank you so much, all of you."},{"time":347242,"text":"FF: Thank you. RD: Thank you. Bye."},{"time":349365,"text":"(Applause)"},{"time":353202,"text":"FF: Thank you. (Applause)"}]}]}